<L>__{interior rachel's hotel night}
<A>__{rachel is packing, folding clothes neatly, precisely, silently all the time a terrible tension in her movements. she tries to close a drawer but it sticks, she keeps trying, then in a sudden rush of fury yanks the drawer free and hurls it across the room. she stands breathing hard.}
